<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-29-0236 </DOCNO><TEXT>The introduction of powered supports in longwall caving face mining atMoonidih Project of M/s. Bharat Coking Coal Limited, located 15 km. fromDhanbad, has revolutionized the system of longwall mining in India. Theconventional longwall caving faces were faced with low productivity andpoor strata concentration due to strata control problems. With the poweredsupport installation in the same geo-mining conditions, the productionto 2700 tons with free O.M.S. up to 45 tons/day. The techniques adoptedin the Moonidih project to control the highly geologically disturbedroof at the power support face are described.</TEXT></DOC>